###SECTION:target_audience
The primary audience strategy targets {{ segments_summary | join("; ") }}. Each of these segments has been identified based on platform data, category purchase intent signals, and first-party customer matching. The highest-priority segments are those with demonstrated conversion intent and CPM efficiency within {{ industry }} category norms.

Secondary audiences will be developed through retargeting (website visitors, social engagers, email list lookalikes) and broad prospecting campaigns designed to expand the top of the funnel. Audience exclusions will be applied systematically to avoid cannibalising organic traffic and existing customer re-purchase cycles.

